Tiger Brands Appoints Olufunke Ighodaro as Its New Chief Financial Officer

-- B y   A n t o n y   S g u a z z i n
-- 
2011-04-12T06:02:29Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-12/tiger-brands-appoints-olufunke-ighodaro-as-its-new-chief-financial-officer.html
Tiger Brands Ltd. (TBS)  said it appointed
Olufunke Ighodaro as its chief financial officer.  Ighodaro is currently chief financial officer of Primedia
Ltd.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Antony Sguazzin at 
 asguazzin@bloomberg.net  